y asked due to its significance in Indian history and its impact on the environment, making it a relevant topic for UPSC and SSC exams.\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n💡 <i>History repeats in exams. Learn from it!</i>\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n#ThisDayInHistory #UPSC #GovtExams")
